thread.title: Max and Bones
thread.title_full: Ocean County Veterinary Hospital reviewed by Max and Bones

author: Max and Bones
title: Max and Bones
text:
Extremely empathic staff! Minimal wait time and left confident that the best care was provided. I'm a new customer, was extremely hesitant since my dog has gone to his vet for 8 years but we live too far these days!
Great experience overall.
